   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Pherous, komogrammateus of Boubastos, to Bakchios and Poseidonios, sitologoi, greeting. The three hundred and fifty, total 350, artabas of wheat returned for me in a report in the month Hathyr I will pay to you at the storehouse at Boubastos by the 15th of the said month, or I will forfeit one and a half times the aforesaid amount. Good-bye. The 20th year, Hathyr 1.</ab>
         </div>
